Archwizard of Valiant Knights</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uizlaaru.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Izlaaru</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/5/01 6:35:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: porting</span><hr size=1> My favorite is when people do this:<br>
I tell group I have to leave because I have to goto Kael.<br>
