    Dusty Grave<br>
Hunk-Erud of Tarew Marr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulimdul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LimDul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/7/01 10:28:02 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.lava.net/~toasty/pictures/limdul.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: porting</span><hr size=1> hehe. The ones where they try to grab you from another zone is irritating.  Not so bad if they come to you.  <br>
<br>
The other times it irks me is when people ask for ports less then 2 zones away.  (eg. asking for a port to Nek from WC)  I have little patience for that, being I remember a time nobody had ports yet and we had to walk everywhere.<br>
<br>
But some folks are learning...if you tell them you're busy, most folks will accept that.<br>
