<br>
I was in a group in Dalnir over the weekend and there was a shadow knight who was getting grief from his family to get off, but he wanted to stay on to level.  Ok, fine.  Just before he had leveled, we lost our monk.  The monk had taken a wrong turn and ended up getting killed by the Overseer.  The Shadow Knight dinged and wanted me to teleport him out right that minute because his family was yelling at him.  Now my group has to do a CR and I teleport him out and there are only 3 people to do it.  I just found it amusing that his family giving him grief wasn't enough to make him log before he dinged, but he had absolutely no patience for a very quick (believe me it was) corpse retrieval for a group member.  We got the corpse and teleported out to DL and now this guy wants us someone to escort him back to the Overthere.  Now this guy has time to spare again!  /boggle<br>
<br>
Another time I was trying to help a friend of a guildie get to DL.  I was hanging out waiting for another guildie and I wasn't planning on being on very long since I had plans in RL so I figured what the hey.  I teleport this guy to DL and he asks me how to get to the Overthere.  I told him I'd run over with him since I needed to change my bind point anyway.  This being my first time through DL, I die in the tunnel.  Ok.  No big deal.  I tp back over to DL and try to drag my corpse only do die again by 2 drolvargs.  Now by no means is this story to rant about the guildie's friend.  Yes, this was my own fault, but I needed to set the stage for what comes up.  A couple of other guildies (one of them being the one I was waiting on in the first place) come over and help me get my corpse.  The rest of my guild was in the process of helping the guy I had tried teleporting in the first place since he made the mistake of trying to help me when I died the second time.  <br>
<br>
Now at this point I am about 30-45 minutes late for my RL plans.  I go over to EC with the guildie I had been waiting on and I get a tell for a tp.  So I tell the person that I am sorry but I am busy and desperately need to camp.  They start giving me grief saying that they can't understand why I can't tp them and then camp.  Boy was this guy's timing bad!  I explain to him that I have just died twice, had to get help doing a CR and am 30-45 minutes late now for my RL plans.  He took the hint and left me alone.  <br>
<br>
